==English==
===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/əˈkweərɪəs/}}
===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[aquarius]]'', "water carrier", from ''[[aqua]]'', "water", + adjective suffix ''[[-arius]]''

===Proper noun===
'''Aquarius'''

#{{constellation}}: A [[constellation]] of the [[zodiac]], supposedly shaped like a water carrier.
#{{astrology}}: The [[Zodiac]] sign for the water carrier, covering January 20 through February 18.

